245
00:17:52,315 --> 00:17:56,403
Benarkah pasien-pasien ini
sedang dirawat di sini?

246
00:17:56,986 --> 00:17:58,154
Sebentar.

247
00:18:02,409 --> 00:18:03,868
INFORMASI PASIEN

248
00:18:04,452 --> 00:18:08,081
